1971;;Minnie and Moskowitz;;American;;John Cassavetes;;John Cassavetes, Gena Rowlands, Seymour Cassel;;romantic comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minnie_and_Moskowitz;;Following a break-up, Minnie Moore, a museum curator, becomes disillusioned by love and meaningful relationships. But after a chance encounter, she meets Seymour Moskowitz, a parking-lot attendant. After this event, Moskowitz falls in love with Minnie, trying desperately to get her to love him back.